node.text:
Thank you all for tuning in on the live chat
Talking about NFTs and how the drop will go. I don't usually do these as you can tell so thanks for being awesome.

Find out all you need via @ivgalleryla
@nifty_gateway

And to all that I missed questions about the industry and advice, I'll do a live just for that soon ❤️

Show her some love and also wish her a happy birthday 🙏😁

node.text:
It was an honour working with you on this @nathanwagner762

With all the things going on in the world we wanted to create something that hopefully inspires hope coming together as one, we the people are the heroes, we the people together, we are strong and learning to work together we are the strongest. Love wins in the end, love can change everything! One love.

Show Nathan some love! 
Please visit my bio link to the song on YouTube, like comment and sub for more collabs coming soon

node.text:
Thought I'd drop this on my birthday.

Been doing some collaborations outside my normal take on art, wanted to go back to writing, lyric writing in this case, so I came up with an idea to work with talented friends bringing them to the spotlight were I can work with theme on a 'No more heroes' themed mixtape.

This one is called 'Stopped waiting for superman' and it was co-written and performed by my friend Anthony Masotti, super talented guy that you should definitely check out.

In a world where we wait for a savior that is no longer around, we have to stand up and be the heroes we seek. @masettipf

check out my channel to here our first track called 'No more Heroes' by Shaxe.
Link in bio

node.text:
Finally dropping this project I have been working on with my homie Shaxe I helped co-write this anti hero track, I feel like superheroes get too much love so this is going the other way, hope you guys enjoy it and if you do, please like and share and don't forget to subscribe also show some love to Shaxe for the crazy skill  @shaxeoriah

YouTube link in my bio - for some Sub love and the lyrics haha
